name: Rise of The Royal Family: Hail to The King
description:
Rise of the Royal Family is a series that tells about family. The struggle of a family in rebuilding and maintaining its integrity which was once destroyed.

-----
Hail to The King.

A new leader has come. He was ready to carry out his duties as king in the royal family. Say, Hail to the king! Hail to the king! Hail to the king!
